iubenda Newsletter Opt-in Booster (iubenda srl)
The iubenda Newsletter Opt-in Booster is a widget provided by iubenda s.r.l. for the collection of consent for email marketing.  
If the User freely decides to provide their email address via the widget, that consent is confirmed with a double opt-in email. Thereafter, the User's consent is recorded in the “iubenda Consent Database”.
If the User withdraws their consent for email marketing using the opt-out method provided by the Owner, the Owner will update this preference in the database.
Personal Data processed: current page; email address; IP address; language; Trackers.
Place of processing:  Italy –
Privacy Policy
.
iubenda Consent Database (iubenda srl)
The iubenda Consent Database allows to store and retrieve records of Users’ consent to the processing of Personal Data, and information and preferences expressed in relation to the provided consent.
In order to do so, it makes use of a Tracker that temporarily stores pending information on the User’s device until it is processed by the API. The Tracker (a browser feature called localStorage) is at that point deleted.
Personal Data processed: Data communicated while using the service; IP address; Trackers.
Place of processing:  Italy –
Privacy Policy
.
